on your phone if you don't have one.

00:22:27.520 --> 00:22:29.270
Start reading your Bible every day and

00:22:29.280 --> 00:22:31.750
ask the Holy Spirit. Say, 'Holy Spirit,

00:22:31.760 --> 00:22:35.669
make this word real to me according

00:22:35.669 --> 00:22:35.679
to

00:22:35.679 --> 00:22:37.630
Ephesians

00:22:37.630 --> 00:22:37.640
1:18.'Remember

00:22:37.640 --> 00:22:41.029
that the eyes of your

00:22:41.039 --> 00:22:42.870
understanding would be enlightened that

00:22:42.880 --> 00:22:46.070
you may know

00:22:47.919 --> 00:22:50.390
the

00:22:50.400 --> 00:22:53.029
hope of His calling on my life. 'What

00:22:53.039 --> 00:22:55.590
is it? Let the eyes of the understanding—the

00:22:55.590 --> 00:22:55.600
word—become

00:22:55.600 --> 00:22:57.909
real to me that it's

00:22:57.919 --> 00:22:58.590
not

00:22:58.590 --> 00:22:58.600
confusing.'Pray

00:22:58.600 --> 00:23:00.710
over your mind. 'I

00:23:00.720 --> 00:23:02.950
understand what I read.'And just feed on

00:23:02.960 --> 00:23:06.390
the word of God daily. Pray daily. Seek

00:23:06.400 --> 00:23:08.149
Him, Jesus, and be real with Him. Don't

00:23:08.159 --> 00:23:09.549
be religious. You don't have to be

00:23:09.559 --> 00:23:12.789
religious. 'Jesus, how are you today?

00:23:12.799 --> 00:23:15.110
How's your day today? I had a rough

00:23:15.120 --> 00:23:17.270
day today. I need you to give me

00:23:17.280 --> 00:23:19.750
strength.'Again,

00:23:19.760 --> 00:23:22.070
you're not going to be

00:23:22.080 --> 00:23:25.029
perfect overnight. Just

00:23:25.039 --> 00:23:27.350
like a child, you learn how to walk,

00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:29.830
you fall when you walk, you get up,

00:23:29.840 --> 00:23:31.909
brush yourself off, and you

00:23:31.919 --> 00:23:33.830
walk some more. That's the same way it

00:23:33.840 --> 00:23:36.149
is to be saved. You fall, you get back

00:23:36.159 --> 00:23:37.909
up, brush yourself off, you keep

00:23:37.919 --> 00:23:40.070
walking it out by faith. That's how we

00:23:40.080 --> 00:23:42.630
live the Christian life. We're

00:23:42.640 --> 00:23:45.909
all a work in progress. Even me, I don't

00:23:45.919 --> 00:23:48.310
have it all together. Even with how

00:23:48.320 --> 00:23:51.190
far I feel like I am with the Lord

00:23:51.200 --> 00:23:53.350
some days, then you have days that you

00:23:53.360 --> 00:23:55.990
go, 'Man, I've got a long way

00:23:55.990 --> 00:23:56.000
to go.'That's

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:58.070
called humility. You just keep yourself

00:23:58.080 --> 00:24:00.789
humble before the Lord. Humble yourself

00:24:00.799 --> 00:24:03.430
underneath the mighty hand of the Lord,

00:24:03.440 --> 00:24:05.590
and in time, He will exalt you.

00:24:05.600 --> 00:24:08.149
So, I just want

00:24:08.159 --> 00:24:11.110
to say I love you all. I pray that

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:14.750
if you got born again

00:24:14.760 --> 00:24:17.510
today, please comment down below if you

00:24:17.520 --> 00:24:19.510
gave your heart to Jesus Christ. Tell

00:24:19.520 --> 00:24:22.149
somebody. Be excited about it. It's an

00:24:22.159 --> 00:24:25.430
exciting time—a transfer from the old

00:24:25.440 --> 00:24:28.390
man to a new man, being born again.

00:24:31.039 --> 00:24:33.190
I hope this blessed you all watching

00:24:33.200 --> 00:24:34.470
this video today.

00:24:36.159 --> 00:24:38.230
God bless you all and thank you for

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:41.679
watching. Bye-bye.

